</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【評測】Beats Fit Pro  開箱 2022 規格，音質，空間音訊，舒適度測試</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/01/24/beats-fit-pro-review/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=beats-fit-pro-review</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jan 2022 15:00:04 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[評測]]></category><category><![CDATA[音樂耳機]]></category><category><![CDATA[Beats Fit Pro]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1081317</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Beats 自從成為 Apple 一份子之後，吸收了各種最新技術，包括同 Apple 手機的簡易連接方式、動態 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Beats 自從成為 Apple 一份子之後，吸收了各種最新技術，包括同 Apple 手機的簡易連接方式、動態空間音訊效果、H1 晶片等等，再推出一些 AirPods 以外不同取向的新產品。今次這款 Beats Fit Pro 運動型耳機，全新設計的耳翼大幅縮小尺寸，令到不常做運動的朋友都同樣適合佩戴，再加上動態空間音訊效果、適應性降噪效果、適應性 EQ 等等，成為一款非常吸引的運動、通勤用無線耳機產品。小編今次會測試各種功能外，最重要還有耳翼的實淨度，還有音色。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC00804 副本-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1082431" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC00804 副本-694x410.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="410" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC00804 副本-694x410.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC00804 副本-1280x756.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC00804 副本-768x453.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC00804 副本-1536x907.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC00804 副本-2048x1209.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC00804 副本-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0015-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081325" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0015-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0015-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0015-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0015-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Beats Fit Pro 同樣秉承了 Beats 耳機的設計風格，醒目的「b」標誌印於機面上。它給人第一個印象，就是機身大小同耳翼都非常細，單邊耳機連耳翼重量只有 5.6g（兩邊耳機合計少於 12g）。這樣輕巧細小的機身，內裡已包含了主動降噪元件、光學感應器、操控按鈕與耳機元件，大可看成是加強了佩戴安定度的 AirPods Pro。</p><h2>評測影片</h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=314&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Funwirehk%2Fvideos%2F884524395577689%2F&amp;show_text=false&amp;width=560&amp;t=0" width="560" height="314" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><h2>小小耳翼做到強力佩戴安全感</h2><p>Beats Fit Pro 耳機最特別是這個小小耳翼。單看這塊小耳翼與按鈕是同一塊膠片，但按鈕部份很實淨，而耳翼部份就有柔軟同具彈性的感覺，令耳機既有一體感設計之餘，實際也各具功能。這個小耳翼的用處，是輕輕貼住人體耳廓凸出來的位置，耳朵剛剛好能包住這個耳翼，令耳機不會輕易跌出來。實際測試耳機的貼合度相當好，跑步、走路都不會有耳機要跌出來的感覺，同時由於耳翼體積細、耳機重量輕，不會有任何特別壓迫感、重量感，能夠與你的耳機連成一體。而且在外觀上，這對耳翼可隱藏到你的外耳廓裡面，不會有很大的一塊凸出來，看上去都非常 smart。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0009-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081329" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0009-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0009-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0009-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0009-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0005.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081321" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0005-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0005-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0005-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0005.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0007-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081322" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0007-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0007-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0007-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0007-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.05.26.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1082796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.05.26-694x453.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="453" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.05.26-694x453.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.05.26-768x501.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.05.26.jpg 1229w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC05909-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1082419" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC05909-694x407.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="407" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC05909-694x407.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC05909-1280x751.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC05909-768x451.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC05909-1536x901.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC05909-2048x1202.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DSC05909-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Beats Fit Pro 機身縮細，也令其充電盒也得到輕量化設計。它的外型有點似加大版的 AirPods Pro 充電盒，但實際重量只有 56g，只比 AirPods Pro 充電盒重 10g，算是比較輕巧的機種。同 AirPods Pro 最大分別是，它用上了 USB Type C 為充電方式（不支援無線充電），並非 Lightning。還好包裝已附隨了一條充電線，所以也沒有特別問題。耳機使用時間為 5 小時，配合充電盒使用時可使用 22 小時，只算是中規中矩的續航力表現。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0013-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081323" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0013-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0013-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0013-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0013-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0012-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081324" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0012-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0012-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0012-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0012-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>實體按鈕 + Android app 支援</h2><p>Beats Fit Pro 耳機每邊都有一個實體操控按鈕，這個設計方便運動型用家確切地知道按動了耳機按鍵。此按鈕可操控通話、控制音樂、切換聆聽模式，啟用語音控制功能等等，另光學感應器可感應用戶是否佩戴上耳機，可自動處理暫停／再次播放與通話等功能。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0002-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1082414" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0002-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0002-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0002-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0002-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>今次 Beats Fit Pro 支援 Android 版 Beats App。用家可在此 App 設定耳朵貼合度測試，更易選擇適合自己的耳塞，APP 內也可自訂按鈕、顯示電池狀態、流暢度更新等等。不過相對 iOS，Android 平台將不會提供「尋找」app 配合、免提聲控「喂 Siri」、音訊分享功能、自動切換功能、iCloud 共享功能等等。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-21-19.02.56.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1082418" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-21-19.02.56-538x580.jpg" alt="" width="538" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-21-19.02.56-538x580.jpg 538w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-21-19.02.56-768x829.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-21-19.02.56.jpg 835w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 538px" /></a></p><h2>主動降噪與 AirPods Pro 同級</h2><p>Beats Fit Pro 支援主動降噪功能，外部兩個以及內部一個咪高風，能夠檢測耳機接收到的噪音，並進行降噪處理。小編在多日測試中，發現它的降噪功能與 AirPods Pro 相若，在地鐵、巴士上都可有效消除引擎的轟轟聲。配合耳機本身的佩戴貼合度與入耳式耳塞，能阻隔部份主動降噪效果較弱的人聲、高頻聲響。在市面上眾多主動降噪耳機產品之中，效果可說是中規中矩。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0010-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081330" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0010-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0010-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0010-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0010-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Beats Fit Pro 耳機支援了 Apple 特有的適應性 EQ 功能，能夠以內部的咪高風感測用戶能夠聽到的聲音，再進行音質調校。只要你的耳機「關閉消噪功能」與「關閉通透模式」的情況下，就會自動啟用適應性 EQ。今次小編的耳機音質測試，也在這個模式下進行。</p><h2>音色表現：傾向重低音與高頻</h2><p>Beats 耳機的重低音效果一向都較 AirPods 系列更強勁。今次也沒有例外，重低音明顯在整體音色中佔了很大的比重，另一方面耳機也增強了高頻方面的表現，耳機整體音色傾向於高頻與低頻，適合收聽強勁節拍的音樂、流行曲使用，也迎合了本耳機運動型的取向。喜歡重低音較強的朋友值得留意本耳機。重低音較強的特性，也令它適合收聽著重低頻的 ASMR 音效。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0018-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081327" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0018-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0018-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0018-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0018-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-21-19.21.35.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1082427" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-21-19.21.35-537x580.jpg" alt="" width="537" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-21-19.21.35-537x580.jpg 537w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-21-19.21.35-768x829.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-21-19.21.35.jpg 832w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 537px" /></a>▲Beats Fit Pro 適合收聽節奏強勁的歌曲，配合了耳機運動型的路線</p><p>雖然耳機重低音較為強勁，但耳機人聲方面只略為靠後，並沒有出現音樂遮掩人聲的情況，Beats Fit Pro 在這方面的平衡做得不錯。由於高頻亦特到強化調音的關係，女聲方面會有一點點毛刺感，較長時間收聽的朋友建議把音量降低一點。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0004-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081328" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0004-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0004-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0004-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/unwire0004-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>不過由於耳機始終把調音取向偏向低頻與高頻，在收聽慢歌、有較多純音樂為襯托的歌曲、較多人聲的演講或清淡節目，音樂的音場、中域的表現、人聲的表現就比較自然。如特別喜愛收聽交響樂、純音樂的朋友，在選購耳機時也最好先試一試。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.05.39.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1082798" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.05.39-694x532.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="532" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.05.39-694x532.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.05.39-1174x900.jpg 1174w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.05.39-768x589.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.05.39.jpg 1264w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲運動型耳機特別適合收聽運動時收聽的 upbeat 歌曲，重低音特別加強，在戶外更容易感受歌曲的強勁感覺</p><h2>空間音訊增添臨場感</h2><p>Beats 耳機都加入了空間音訊的支援，在 iOS 的耳機音量選單裡面便可開啟。開啟後系統會建立一個音場空間，耳機內的偵測器偵測到用家的頭部活動，更會動態追隨「聲源位置」。假設演奏者在你的面前演奏，而你的頭顱向左轉的話，聲音便會加強偏向右方耳機傳來的感覺，讓你有種身處於演奏空間的感覺。無論是音樂或者清淡節目，都會加強了臨場感覺。用戶亦可關閉「追蹤頭部」功能，只擴闊聲音驅場感。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.19.24.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1082802" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.19.24-539x580.jpg" alt="" width="539" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.19.24-539x580.jpg 539w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.19.24-768x827.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.19.24.jpg 835w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 539px" /></a></p><h2>總結：輕盈而佩戴感十足的運動型耳機</h2><p>總括來說，Beats Fit Pro 耳機是一款體積令人有點驚喜的運動型耳機，輕盈細細的機身卻有非常不錯的佩戴安全感，強烈運動不會引致耳機跌落，甚至移位也不會。確保你的強勁音樂不會漏聲，強勁重低音得到更好的保留。它的全面 Apple 功能例如連接便利性、共享音訊、「喂 Siri」便利性、空間音響效果、通透模式、「尋找」耳機功能等等，令它成為更好用的運動耳機。如果你嘗試過耳機音色取向，又覺得適合的話，就非常值得入手。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.04.55.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1082799" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.04.55-694x405.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="405" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.04.55-694x405.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.04.55-1280x748.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.04.55-768x449.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-24-18.04.55.jpg 1445w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
